OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FA transgender woman from West Sussex
OL,7,Fwho relies on hormone therapy
OL,8,Ftreatment says she feels discriminated
OL,9,Fagainst - after her GP can no longer
OL,10,Fsupply it to her.
OL,12,FJoanne Monck OBE has been told by New
OL,13,FPond Surgery in Lancing to travel to a
OL,14,Fgender specialist clinic in Brighton.
OL,16,FShe received an OBE in 2021 for her
OL,17,Fwork championing transgender rights
OL,18,Fand feels she should be able to access
OL,19,Fit from her GP still.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
