PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FJoanne told ITV News Meridian: "It's
OL,7,Ftotally wrong. I've been having my
OL,8,Fprescription from my GP for 12 years.
OL,9,FWhy have they stopped giving it to me?
OL,10,FWhy do I have to go to a gender
OL,11,Fidentity clinic now to get it? I was
OL,12,Ffurious. I know my gender."
OL,14,FJoanne was born as David and spent 58
OL,15,Fyears of her life hiding who she was
OL,16,Fbefore beginning hormone therapy
OL,17,Ffollowed by gender surgery in 2017.
OL,26,@nD@`OUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
