PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FShe now takes hormone replacement
OL,7,Ftherapy, or HRT, which involves
OL,8,Freceiving a regular a dose of estrogen
OL,9,Fto bring about desired changes in the
OL,10,Fbody.
OL,12,FIt's a situation that transgender
OL,13,Fcharities say is becoming more
OL,14,Fcommonplace across the country.
OL,16,FChay Brown from the charity Trans
OL,17,FActual said: "We found that trans
OL,18,Fpeople often avoid having to the GP
OL,19,Ffor other medical appointments and and
OL,20,Foften have little confidence or
OL,21,Fthey're not very confident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,F"They feel healthcare professionals
OL,7,Faren't going to understand their needs
OL,8,Fand this is coming from experiences
OL,9,Flike being refused their hormone
OL,10,Fprescription and just generally
OL,11,Ffeeling like they're getting poorer
OL,12,Ftreatment than they would get if they
OL,13,Fweren't trans."
OL,15,FNHS England say there are shared care
OL,16,Fagreements between the specialist
OL,17,Fgender clinics where the person is
OL,18,Fassessed and diagnosed and local GPs
OL,19,Fwho administer and monitor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FThey say a recent review into adult
OL,7,Fgender services highlighted how: "Many
OL,8,FGPs feel they lack the appropriate
OL,9,Fexpertise to support this population.
OL,10,FSome lack confidence due to their
OL,11,Flimited experience in this area and
OL,12,Fthe complexity of prescribing."
OL,26,@oD@bOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
