PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FIn a statement, Joanne's GP surgery,
OL,7,FNew Pond Surgery in Lancing, said: "To
OL,8,Fensure the highest standards of
OL,9,Fpatient safety, and following a
OL,10,Fprescribing audit and updated
OL,11,Fprescribing guidance, we will now only
OL,12,Fprovide prescriptions for patients who
OL,13,Fneed this care who are also supported
OL,14,Fby an Enhanced Shared Care Agreement
OL,15,F(ESCA).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,F"All NHS prescribing in this area
OL,7,Fshould be happening via shared care
OL,8,Fagreements - between the specialist
OL,9,Fgender clinics where the person was
OL,10,Fassessed and diagnosed, and local GPs
OL,11,Fwho administer and monitor. This is
OL,12,Fnot in-place with this patient at this
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"However, we will continue to
OL,16,Fprescribe until the specialist team
OL,17,Ftakes over care, so there is no break
OL,18,Fin treatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,F"The decision has been made to ensure
OL,7,Fall patients receive care that is
OL,8,Fsafe, appropriate, and delivered by
OL,9,Fteams with the right expertise.
OL,11,F"Our surgery is not currently signed
OL,12,Fup to the NHS Sussex TNBI
OL,13,F(Transgender, NonBinary and Intersex)
OL,14,FLocally Commissioned Service.
OL,16,F"Participation in this service is
OL,17,Fvoluntary, and we are not enrolled
OL,18,Fbecause we do not have the specialist
OL,19,Fskills required to provide this level
OL,20,Fof care safely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,F"As a result, we are unable to offer
OL,7,Fthe specialist TNBI services provided
OL,8,Fthrough this pathway. The nearest
OL,9,Fspecialist clinic is located in
OL,10,FBrighton."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
