FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FNHS England say the adult gender
OL,7,Fservices review recommended that NHS
OL,8,FEngland and ICBs should work with
OL,9,Fadult GDCs and GP representative
OL,10,Fbodies to establish sustainable local
OL,11,Farrangements for hormone prescribing
OL,12,Fand access to longer-term health
OL,13,Fmonitoring, including the development
OL,14,Fof local hormone prescribing pilots,
OL,15,Fpotentially using the GPs with
OL,16,FExtended Roles model or other local
OL,17,Fmodels of care; every ICB ensuring
OL,18,Fthere is local primary care support
OL,19,Ffor the prescription and monitoring of
OL,20,Fhormones for their population; and
OL,21,FGDCs managing hormone prescribing for
OL,22,Fpatients for a minimum of 1 year until
OL,23,Flevels are stable, before discharging
OL,24,Fpatients to primary care.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773328287
OL,3,CTransgender woman's frustration as GP
OL,4,Crefuses her hormone therapy treatment
OL,6,FNHS England is taking forward those
OL,7,Frecommendations as part of the ongoing
OL,8,Fimprovement programme.
OL,10,FHormone replacement therapy (HRT) is a
OL,11,Ftreatment used to help menopause
OL,12,Fsymptoms. It replaces the hormones
OL,13,Foestrogen and progesterone, which fall
OL,14,Fto low levels as you approach the
OL,15,Fmenopause, but it's also used by trans
OL,16,Fwomen to induce feminine physical
OL,17,Ftraits.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
